      "description": "Validation result for absolute hemolysis index predictions across 5 VAD operating points. The supporting activity employed a high-fidelity numerical simulation with Monte Carlo uncertainty propagation, which the assessment team argues provides evidence equivalent in epistemic value to a physical bench experiment given the difficulty of isolating hemolysis contributions experimentally. All 5 operating points show predicted hemolysis index within the claimed acceptance band.",
